WEBVTT

00:00:00.271 --> 00:00:08.072
Integrating self-awareness, conflict agility, and empathy into a coherent vision creates a powerful impact.

00:00:08.652 --> 00:00:13.553
Reflect on the practical payoff of having a personal corporate leadership philosophy.

00:00:14.213 --> 00:00:19.714
It provides a clear, actionable framework for navigating complex global environments.

00:00:20.815 --> 00:00:29.436
The future belongs to leaders who balance the cold calculus of technological scaling with the warm reality of human sustainability.

00:00:30.878 --> 00:00:37.498
Engineering the optimal climate for teams and leading with purpose is the ultimate performance of understanding.
